-- Newmont Plans to Boost African Gold Output to 1.5 Million Ounces by 2015
-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 2011-02-08T10:19:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-08/newmont-plans-to-boost-african-gold-output-to-1-5-million-ounces-by-2015.html
  Newmont Mining Corp . plans to boost
gold production from its African region to 1.5 million ounces by
2015, from about 500,000 ounces now, Adriaan Van Kersen,
regional group executive, said in a speech at the Mining Indaba
conference in  Cape Town  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
